The '''''Saber''-class assault tank''' line was a series of medium, ground-based combat [[Hovertank/Legends|fighter tanks]] produced by [[Rothana Heavy Engineering/Legends|Rothana Heavy Engineering]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

==History==
The ''Saber''-class was first introduced with the [[TX-130 Saber-class fighter tank/Legends|TX-130S]] model early in the Clone Wars. These [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] fighter tanks were piloted by [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] and [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] alike, most notably during the [[Dark Reaper crisis]]. During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] era, Rothana Heavy Engineering produced the [[TX-130T fighter tank|TX-130T]] and [[2-M Saber-class repulsor tank/Legends|2-M]] variants. The [[Scout-class 2-M repulsor tank/Legends|SC2-M Repulsor Tank]] was an scout variant of the 2-M. It was a ''Saber''-class tank, but not a [[Hovertank/Legends|fighter tank]].

